Modify Related Attributes

You can modify related attributes while building your segments and activations or after you’ve saved them. You can use up to 100 activations with related attributes. After reaching that limit, you can choose to delete related attributes from existing activations or create activations with only direct attributes.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience
In Data Cloud, click Segments, and select a segment.
Under Activations, click  and select Edit.
In Edit Activation, click Next.
To add or delete related attributes:
Click Add Attributes.
Add related attributes from objects in the same path.
Click the X for the related attribute you want to delete and confirm the deletion.
Click Save.
NOTE If you delete all attributes from the furthest DMO in the path, and attributes from that DMO are used to filter, then all filters are deleted.
